    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Hubertus">Upperto</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Stephanus">Stefani</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Ardefunsus">Ardifusi</name></persName>
                        ricevono da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>,
                        gratia Dei huius sancte Lucanem ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine ad laborandum et
                        gubernandum seo meliorandum (…), duo petiis de terris illis, ultra <rs
                            key="#Rivers">fluvio Auserclo</rs>, in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3322">Spardacho</placeName>, qui fuerunt domnicatas,
                        pertenentes <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Churches">Sancti Vincentii et
                            Fridiani</orgName>, sita <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4">foras
                                <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista Lucense</placeName>, qui est de
                        suppotestate ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, qui una ex ipse petia de terra est tenentes uno caput
                        in terra et vinea <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">Sancti
                            Valentini</orgName>, alio caput tenet in terra ipsius eccl(esie) vestre
                            <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            >Sancti Fridiani</orgName>, quas <persName><name ref="Mannulus"
                                >Mannulo</name></persName> ad manus ecc. (…) et in aliquantulo in
                            <rs>terra</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3308"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Monasteries">Sancti Petri que
                            dicitur Bellerifonsi</orgName>, lato uno tenet in <rs>terra</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/603"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Monasteries">Sancti Petri</orgName>
                        sito <placeName ref="#places/336" key="#Monasteries">Campo
                            Maiore</placeName>, alio lato tenet in terra suprascripte eccl(esie)
                        Sancti Valentini et in terra Georgii not; et ille alia petia de terra et
                        insula insimul amembratas tenentes uno caput in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Emperor/king">terra
                            domni regi</rs> et in terra suprascripte eccl(esie) vestre Sancti
                        Fridiani, quas iam dicto Mannulo ad manus ecc. (…), alio caput cum uno lato
                        tenet in terra et vinea suprascripti Georgii not et iam dicto monast(erii)
                        Sancti Petri de Campo Maiore, alio lato tenet in fluvio Auserclo (…) cum
                        cesis et fossis; (…). Censo: ad pars ipsius eccl(esie) vestre Sancti
                        Fridiani, per sing(ulos) annos (…) tertia parte omni labore, quas Dominus
                        exinde donare dignatus fuerit; et quando ibidem misso vestro super trituram
                        venerit, nos eos recipere ecc. et ipsam vestram portionem de predicto labore
                        per sing(ulos) annos nos eum traere et aducere faciamus hic Luca ad ipso
                        domo vestro Sancti Martini tantum (…). Pena: argen(tum) solid(os)
                        quinquaginta (…). Actum Luca. Scrive: Rachifonsum not </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
